### ============================================
### 3. MEMBER
### ============================================

### 3.1 - Get semua member
GET {{baseUrl}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.2 - Get member dengan filter search
GET {{baseUrl}}/members?search=budi&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.3 - Get member filter by status aktif
GET {{baseUrl}}/members?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.4 - Get member filter by kelas
GET {{baseUrl}}/members?category=VIP
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.5 - Get statistik member (untuk dashboard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.6 - Buat member baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso",
  "phone": "081234567890",
  "classCategory": "Basic",
  "startDate": "2025-01-01",
  "durationDays": 30,
  "reason": "Pendaftaran manual"
}

###

### 3.7 - Buat member kelas VIP
POST {{baseUrl}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Siti Rahayu",
  "phone": "082345678901",
  "classCategory": "VIP",
  "startDate": "2025-01-01",
  "durationDays": 30,
  "reason": "Member VIP baru"
}

###

### 3.8 - Update member (ganti memberId dulu)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso Updated",
  "phone": "081234567890",
  "classCategory": "Intermediate"
}

###

### 3.9 - Perpanjang durasi member
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/extend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "durationDays": 30,
  "reason": "Perpanjangan manual oleh admin"
}

###

### 3.10 - Hapus member
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.11 - Export Excel (akan download file)
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


